TITLE: Testing HTTP Service with JUnit 5 and Vert.x
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the new vertx-junit5 module to test a HTTP service verticle. The test deploys a SampleVerticle, makes 10 concurrent HTTP requests, and verifies the responses using AssertJ assertions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vert-x3/vertx-web-site/blob/master/src/site/blog/posts/releases/2018-02-13-vertx-3.5.1-release.md#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
