LANGUAGE: groovy
CODE:
```
def server = vertx.createNetServer()

server.connectHandler { sock ->
    sock.dataHandler { buffer ->
        if (!sock.writeQueueFull) {
            sock.write(buffer)
        } else {
            sock.pause()
        }
    }
}.listen(1234, "localhost")
