TITLE: Implementing Order Submission in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Handles order submission by sending order data to MongoDB persistor with session authentication
SOURCE: https://github.com/vert-x3/vertx-web-site/blob/master/src/main/vertx2/vertx1x_docs/docs_md/groovy_web_tutorial.md#2025-04-19_snippet_9

